Seq1.ReceiverContent: Good afternoon, this is Carl from Stanley Practice. How may I assist you today?

Seq2.CallerContent: Hi, I was calling to see if there were any cancellations. I made an appointment this morning, but it's not for like two weeks. And I was just seeing if anyone canceled for tomorrow.
Seq2.ReceiverContent: Tomorrow, one moment, let me check on it.

Seq4.ReceiverContent: Would you like to come to the office in the afternoon after 2 p.m.?

Seq6.ReceiverContent: Okay, one moment. May I know your date of birth, please?

Seq10.ReceiverContent: Okay, one moment. But you have made an appointment on 13th of October for a tele-visit, am I correct?

Seq11.ReceiverContent: But this is only for an office visit to meet the doctor in person.

Seq12.CallerContent: That's fine. I can be there in person. I just, I can't go without my medicine for that long. And I thought I still had one at the pharmacy and I don't, so I need to come in.

Seq13.ReceiverContent: Okay, one moment. So, just to confirm, I have rescheduled your appointment to tomorrow at 2 p.m. for an office visit.

Seq15.ReceiverContent: Is there anything else that I may have to do with?

Seq16.CallerContent: No, that is all. Thank you so much.

Seq17.ReceiverContent: Thank you for calling Crosswinds Valley Practice. You have a great day.
